                    <div class="step-number">5</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Testing & Quality Assurance</h3>
                        <p>We conduct comprehensive testing to ensure all functions work correctly, integrations are seamless, and the system meets your requirements.</p>
                        <ul class="step-deliverables">
                            <li><i class="fas fa-vial"></i> Test Cases & Scripts</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-user-check"></i> User Acceptance Testing</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i> Performance Testing</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-bug"></i> Issue Resolution</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="process-step" data-step="6">
                    <div class="step-number">6</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Training & Deployment</h3>
                        <p>We train your team and deploy the system with careful planning to ensure a smooth transition and minimal disruption.</p>
                        <ul class="step-deliverables">
                            <li><i class="fas fa-user-graduate"></i> Training Programs</li>
